name: HauntPortal
summary: Partnered with Top Haunts in the U.S, AUGXIST: HauntPortal is a 3D360 Virtual Reality Platform. Groups of up to 6 Users can enjoy terrifying Cinematic VR content based on the characters, stories, locations and brands of Haunted Attraction Events such as Pennhurst Asylum, The Mortuary, Woods of Terror, and more!
